data.title: Former Dallasite and Monkee Michael Nesmith on His Surprising Career in Film and Being Awarded at The Kessler
data.meta_description: Michael Nesmith will be back in Dallas Saturday, Oct. 1, to accept the Ernie Kovacs award from Dallas Video Fest at The Kessler.
